text: Antonia Papandreou-Suppappola from the Arizona State University, Tempe, AZ was named Fellow of the Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers (IEEE) in 2013 for contributions to applications of time-frequency signal processing. == References == Category:Fellow Members of the IEEE Category:Living people Category:Arizona State University faculty Category:University of Rhode Island alumni Category:21st-century American engineers Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
